OL,3,CFrench lawmakers approve social media
OL,4,Cban for children under 15
OL,6,FFrance has passed a bill banning under-
OL,7,F15s from social media, which, among
OL,8,Fother measures, will prohibit mobile
OL,9,Fphones in schools.
OL,11,FLawmakers approved the legislation on
OL,12,FMonday, just days after the UK's House
OL,13,Fof Lords backed a social media ban for
OL,14,Funder-16s.
OL,16,FThe bill passed through the divided
OL,17,FFrench National Assembly by 130 votes
OL,18,Fto 121 and will be discussed by the
OL,19,FFrench Senate in the coming weeks.
