OL,6,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron has
OL,7,Fasked for the legislation to be fast-
OL,8,Ftracked, so that it could be in place
OL,9,Fby the start of the next school year
OL,10,Fin September.
OL,12,F"Banning social media for those under
OL,13,F15: this is what scientists recommend,
OL,14,Fand this is what the French people are
OL,15,Foverwhelmingly calling for," he said
OL,16,Fafter the vote.
