OL,3,CFrench lawmakers approve social media
OL,4,Cban for children under 15
OL,6,F"Because our children's brains are not
OL,7,Ffor sale ` neither to American
OL,8,Fplatforms nor to Chinese networks.
OL,9,FBecause their dreams must not be
OL,10,Fdictated by algorithms."
OL,12,FThe bill complies with the European
OL,13,FUnion's Digital Services Act, designed
OL,14,Fto keep internet users safe.
OL,16,FFrance's health watchdog reported in
OL,17,FDecember that 90 per cent of children
OL,18,Fbetween 12 and 17 years old use
OL,19,Fsmartphones daily to access the
OL,20,Finternet.
