OL,6,FAround 58 per cent of them used their
OL,7,Fdevices for social networks.
OL,9,FThe report highlighted the harmful
OL,10,Feffects this could have, including
OL,11,Freduced self-esteem and increased
OL,12,Fexposure to harmful content.
OL,14,FThis is not the first time France has
OL,15,Facted to limit children's phone use.
OL,16,FIn 2018, the country passed a law
OL,17,Fbanning phone use in all primary and
OL,18,Fmiddle schools.
