OL,3,CFrench lawmakers approve social media
OL,4,Cban for children under 15
OL,6,FLast year, Australia became the first
OL,7,Fcountry to restrict children's online
OL,8,Faccess.
OL,10,FFrom December 10, young Australians
OL,11,Fwere blocked from accessing sites such
OL,12,Fas TikTok, Instagram and Snapchat.
OL,14,FThe Australian government says almost
OL,15,Ffive million social media accounts
OL,16,Fhave been deactivated after the law
OL,17,Fcame into effect.
